{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 15,
  "title": "第十五章（不盈）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "古之善為道者，微眇玄達，深不可志。夫唯不可志，故強為之容。"
    },
    {
      "text": "曰：與呵，亓若冬涉水。猶呵，亓若畏四鄰。儼呵，亓若客。渙呵，亓若淩澤。沌呵，亓若樸。湷呵，亓若濁。莊呵，亓若浴。"
    },
    {
      "text": "濁而情之余清，安以重之余生。"
    },
    {
      "text": "葆此道不欲盈。夫唯不欲盈，是以能敝而不成。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 29,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂得道之君也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 29,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "玄，天也。言其志節玄妙，精與天通也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 29,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道德深遠，不可識知，內視若盲，反聽若聾，莫知所長。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 29,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂下句也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "舉事輒加重慎與。與兮若冬涉川，心難之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其進退猶猶如拘制，若人犯法，畏四鄰知之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "如客畏主人，儼然無所造作也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "渙者，解散。釋者，消亡。除情去欲，日以空虛。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "敦者，質厚。朴者，形未分。內守精神，外無文采也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "曠者，寬大。谷者，空虛。不有德功名，無所不包也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "渾者，守本真，濁者，不照然。與眾合同，不自專也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孰，誰也。誰能知水之濁止而靜之，徐徐自清也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "誰能安靜以久，徐徐以長生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 21,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "保此徐生之道，不欲奢泰盈溢。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 21,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫為不盈滿之人，能守蔽不為新成。蔽者，匿光榮也。新成者，貴功名。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "冬之涉川，豫然若欲度、若不欲度，其情不可得見之貌也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "四鄰合攻中央之主，猶然不知所趣向者也。上德之人，其端兆不可覩，德趣不可見，亦猶此也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 56,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "凡此諸若，皆言其容象不可得而形名也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫晦以理物則得明，濁以靜物則得清，安以動物則得生，此自然之道也。孰能者，言其難也。徐者，詳慎也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 21,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "盈必溢也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 21,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "蔽，覆蓋也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
